Mod.name: Acolyte Fight 7.0
Mod.author: Mr7
Mod.description: Welcome to The M-7's first mod

flamestrike.name: Fireslice
flamestrike.description: Throw a heated dagger that will cut right thru players.

kamehameha.name: Lazer Beam
kamehameha.description: Unleash a beam so powerful it wipes out all projectiles.

effects.title: Interruptible
effects.text: If you take an enemy hit, Lazer Beam will be interrupted.

shield.description: Reflect away projectile attacks. Ineffective against area-of-effect spells or Ghostball.

voidRush.description: For 3 seconds, increase movement speed 85%, and also become immune to damage from the void.

Stalk.description: This projectile will follow your enemy redirecting his movment.

Cloak.name: Cloak
Cloak.description: Press button to activate and press button again to cancel. Transform into a projectile and reappear as you wish. If you hit a player they will take damage and you will reappear.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

StarBomb.description: Shot an explosive star at your enemey that will redirect at the location of your cursor when you shot. If you or an opponent shoots the star it will explode.
StarBomb.name: Starbomb

Transaber.name: Transport Saber
Transaber.description: For 1 second you will summon a sword that teleports your oppenets and enemys projectiles into the location you striked them at. The faster you swing, the farther they go.

effects.title: Detach
effects.text: Lightsaber cuts through any Links or Grapples.

effects.title: Slow
effects.text: Your movement speed is reduced 50% when casting Lightsaber.

IceBlast.description: A delayed explosion of frost that will slow down your enemy by 70%.
IceBlast.name: Iceblast

Fire Shard.description: A large shard of fire, dealing high damage headed right towards your enemies.
Fire Shard.name: Fire Shard

HealthOrb.description: Slow moving orb that does no damage but gives huge health gain when oppenet is hit.
HealthOrb.name: Health Orb

Orbs.name: Zapping Orb
Orbs.description: A quick electirc orb circling around you. Get close to an enemy to stun them for 0.5 seconds.

Flame.name: Flamestrike
Flame.description: Send a flame twoard your enemies that will do burning damage.

TrapShot.description: At first a normal projecitle, but on contact with opponent or object it will turn into an ensare trapping your enemies.

effects.title: Silence
effects.text: Your enemy will be unable to cast spells for 0.75 seconds.

effects.title: Recharge
effects.text: If it hits, reduces cooldowns for all your spells except Ensnare by 4 seconds.

Grasp of Healing.name: Hook of Healing
Grasp of Healing.description: A hook that latches on to your enemies and gives you their health.

grappled.name: Drag
grappled.description: Hold the button to Drag. You quickly drag yourself to your opponent!

Ghostball.name: Ghostball
Ghostball.description: Fire a mystikal ball that travels thru objects and projectiles

BodyShock.name: BodyShock
BodyShock.description: Get in close to shock your enemys with electricly coming from your body

effects.title: Fast
effects.text: Gain a 15% movement speed bonus for 3 seconds (even if you miss).

KnockBolt.name: KnockBolt
KnockBolt.description: Quickly send out four powerful energy bolts. Each bolt deals 2 damage and has little knockback. The more bolts that hit, the more knockback will be taken.

LightStamp.name: LightStamp
LightStamp.description: Place a lightbulb in your exact positon. Dealing damage when enemies come into contact with it. The lightbulb shatters when the middle is touched by an opponent or within 4 seconds.'

telep0rt.description: Teleport to a nearby location. Get close, or get away.

effects.title: Weak
effects.text: For 0.25 seconds after teleporting, you will only deal 25% damage and cannot deal fatal damage.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

Shine Slice.name: Shine Slice
Shine Slice.description: Charge and cut right thru enemys and objects. Beaware you are NOT immune to damage.

phaseout.name: Phase Shift
phaseout.description: Hold down the button to disappear from the world for up to 0.75 seconds. While phased shifted, you cannot be hurt, but you also cannot cast spells. Phase shift also cancels all knockback. Phase shift takes longer to cooldown the longer you stay in phase shift.

Lazer.name: Lazer
Lazer.description: Shoot a quick, small, high damage lazer.

Fire Mines.name: Fire Mines
Fire Mines.description: Mark out your territory with some Fire Mines. Upon contact your enemies will start to slowy burn. Fire mines will also burn certain projectiles, but the mines will burnout if you walk to far away.

Frostbite.description: Fire a ray of ice that slows down an opponent by 20%.
Frostbite.name: frostbite

Stun Shot.name: StunShot
Stun Shot.description: Fast firing bolt that will leave your enemy stunned.

K Mines.name: Freezing Mines
K Mines.description: Mark your terriotry with Freezing Mines. These mines freeze upon impact by 60%

Director.name: Lightwave
Director.description: Fire a projectile that will be mimicked by your cursor.

Seekers.name: Backshot
Seekers.description: Gain a boost from firing 3 bolts from your back.

OutBreak.name: OutBreak
OutBreak.description: A toxic explosion forming 16 bolts of toxic energy from the center of your player.

Cleanse.name: Cleanse
Cleanse.description: Instanly remove all positive and negative effects.

Void Run.name: Void Run
Void Run.description: Run under the void for 2 seconds, being immune to all types of damage or effects.

effects.title: Cleanse
effects.text: Clears all positive and negative effects.

effects.title: Void recharge
effects.text: Cools down 2x faster when in the void.

C Mines.name: Entrapment
C Mines.description: Quickly rotate throwing energy mines all around you. These mines do litte damage, but high knockback.

Icicles.name: Icicles
Icicles.description: Fire 3 icicles that will slide back your enemy, as if their sliding on ice.

Radiation.name: GammaBall
Radiation.description: A toxic ball that will drain enemeys HP when their in the radius zone.

-NU-Ricocheter.name: Ricocheter
-NU-Ricocheter.description: Toss bouncer daggers that reflect off of objects and projectiles.

Ricochet.description: A projectile that reflects off of everthing.
Ricochet.name: Ricochet

whirlwind1.name: Black hole
whirlwind1.description: Quickly charge up a blackhole that will attract enemies projectiles.

effects.title: Attrack.
effects.text: All mines will be atttracked to the center including your own.

Shockwave.name: ShockWave
Shockwave.description: Create a shockwave forcing back enemies and projectiles.

dragonsBreath.name: Dragon's Breath
dragonsBreath.description: Splatter out a wave of inferno that came from the breath of a dragon. Opponents will take damage and be set on fire.

effects.title: Silence
effects.text: Your enemy will be unable to cast spells for 1 seconds.

Wrecking Ball.description: Swing a Wrecking ball at your enemies! Rotate your cursor in a circular motion around your body to get the wreckign ball goin'.
